{"tid":893281,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"一個post就睇得出香港有唔少文盲話要廢中文科，實情就係自己廢又唔想讀中文","createTime":"2018-11-07T13:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T06:52:41.000Z","uid":34884,"like":113,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"57540274b85d2dc9f1b650bb9b216fbccbbcbe6b","tid":893281,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:29:20.000Z","msg":"又話中文係母語，唔使讀都識<br />\n但連『知己』同『好朋友』呢啲咁簡單既詞語都分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個語感稍為正常少少都睇得出有咩分別啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地考評局係話你用字唔準確<br />\n成班人喺到盲屌考評局<br />\n屌 唔該你地屌就屌得有水平啲啦<br />\n<br />\n自問自己中文水平唔高<br />\n但起碼好過班盲屌既人<br />\n你地真係好撚羞家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲下真係會錯把馮京當馬涼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個post入面盲屌既人唔止兩三個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n考評局指「知己」不等同「好朋友」、「禁區」不等同「限制」、「重遊」不等同「再臨」<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bLxoQS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bLxoQS</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8061d96857849eb070f7c50e78759de85752e9f","tid":893281,"uid":135445,"like":15,"dislike":37,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"唔支持廢<br />\n但覺得應該改做2322<br />\n利：中文4"},{"pid":"8347deee23e7944b0b7e4a0d2ea2cf6aa325a575","tid":893281,"uid":191352,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:31:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db81a95cb141974ddfec22037ec40c4867a185c0","tid":893281,"uid":135445,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:31:54.000Z","msg":"依家班00後媳婦同老婆都唔識分<br />\n可能睇太多av<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0e6c98e47ccf7fd096b75fcd28da8ca1083c1e","tid":893281,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:37:48.000Z","msg":"廢中文果堆好明顯係壞腦"},{"pid":"a9dc785887385abf2a0b47116d2fc0500a305cc5","tid":893281,"uid":220458,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quo